    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;necromancy&nbsp;[curse];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;druid 5, hunter 5, mesmerist 4, witch 5;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a flask of seawater)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;one creature<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;permanent<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You inflict a curse of the roiling sea upon the target, making it permanently sickened. Anytime the target is on or in the water more than a mile from shore, it also becomes staggered with seasickness. This curse cannot be dispelled, though <i>remove curse</i> or <i>break enchantment</i> can negate it.</p>\n</div>\n"
